bookTitle: Locke & Key, Vol. 4: Keys to the Kingdom
plot: Joe Hill and Gabriel Rodriguez's Locke & Key unwinds into its fourth volume in Keys to the Kingdom. With more keys making themselves known, and the depths of the Locke family's mystery ever-expanding, Dodge's desperation to end his shadowy quest drives the inhabitants of Keyhouse ever closer to a revealing conclusion.
characters: Tyler Locke, Kinsey Locke, Bode Locke
